data.content: Yes, Coco is an animated musical fantasy film released in 2017 and tells the story of a 12-year-old boy named Miguel who dreams of becoming an accomplished musician like his idol Ernesto de la Cruz.

Yes, I know the movie Coco. It is an animated musical fantasy film produced by Pixar Animation Studios and released by Walt Disney Pictures. It follows a 12-year-old boy named Miguel who dreams of becoming an accomplished musician like his idol Ernesto de la Cruz, despite his family's generations-old ban on music.
